### Dashboard API Tests
### Test all dashboard endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Fee Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/fee-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Fee Statistics with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/fee-stats?academicYear=2025-2026&quota=puducherry-ut
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Recent Payments (default 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/recent-payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Recent Payments with Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/recent-payments?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Recent Payments Filtered
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/recent-payments?limit=20&academicYear=2025-2026&quota=nri
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Defaulters (default 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/defaulters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Defaulters with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/defaulters?limit=20&minDaysOverdue=30&department=Medicine
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Collection Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/collection-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Collection Summary with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/collection-summary?startDate=2025-10-01&endDate=2025-10-17
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get Collection Summary for Academic Year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/collection-summary?academicYear=2025-2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Complete Dashboard Overview (All data in one call)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Dashboard Overview with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/overview?academicYear=2025-2026&department=Medicine&quota=puducherry-ut
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Test without Authentication (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/fee-stats

### 14. Get Fee Statistics - All Quotas Comparison
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/fee-stats?academicYear=2025-2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Get Defaulters - High Priority (>60 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/defaulters?minDaysOverdue=60&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
